      },
      {
        "_key": "ff915832897a",
        "_type": "unorderedListItem",
        "description": "Depending on your work, you might get paid leave during this time."
      }
    ],
    "finalParagraph": "If you were exposed to COVID-19 while at work, you may file WCB paperwork and apply for paid leave.\n\nFor more information, please refer to the following fact sheet and additional documentation:",
    "mainParagraph": "Due to COVID-19, there is a pandemic in Canada. COVID-19 affects worker safety.\n\nAs a workplace hazard, it is called a biological hazard. Although employers must make work safe for workers during this time, many workers, such as health care aides, are at more risk because of workplace contact and poor safety rules.",
    "subHeading": "What if I test positive for COVID-19?"
  },
